@startuml
title Runtime + Gateway Component View

top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
hide stereotype

actor "Operator" as Operator

component "web_ui/frontend" as WebUI
component "Makefile / scripts / ros2 launch" as CLI
component "asr_launch\nfull_stack_dev + gateway_with_runtime" as Launch

package "Gateway Boundary" {
  component "asr_gateway/api.py\nFastAPI endpoints" as GatewayAPI
  component "GatewayRosClient\nRuntimeObserver" as GatewayROS
}

package "Runtime Pipeline" {
  component "audio_input_node" as AudioInput
  component "audio_preprocess_node" as AudioPreprocess
  component "vad_segmenter_node" as VadNode
  component "asr_orchestrator_node" as Orchestrator
}

package "Provider Resolution" {
  component "ProviderManager" as ProviderManager
  component "AsrProviderAdapter" as ProviderAdapter
  component "Backend / SDK wrapper" as Backend
}

database "configs/runtime\nconfigs/providers" as Configs
database "secrets/refs + env" as Secrets
queue "ROS2 topics + services + actions" as RosGraph
cloud "Local model / cloud speech API" as SpeechEngine

Operator --> WebUI : browser control
Operator --> CLI : launch and scripts
CLI --> Launch : start stack

Launch --> AudioInput
Launch --> AudioPreprocess
Launch --> VadNode
Launch --> Orchestrator
Launch --> GatewayAPI

WebUI --> GatewayAPI : HTTP / JSON
GatewayAPI --> GatewayROS : translate UI requests

GatewayAPI --> Configs : list / validate / resolve profiles
GatewayAPI --> Secrets : inspect and validate secret refs
GatewayROS --> Orchestrator : runtime control services

AudioInput --> RosGraph : publish AudioChunk(raw)
RosGraph --> AudioPreprocess : subscribe raw audio

AudioPreprocess --> RosGraph : publish AudioChunk(preprocessed)
RosGraph --> VadNode : segmented mode input
RosGraph --> Orchestrator : provider_stream input

VadNode --> RosGraph : publish SpeechActivity
VadNode --> RosGraph : publish AudioSegment
RosGraph --> Orchestrator : speech segments

Orchestrator --> ProviderManager : create_from_profile(...)
ProviderManager --> Configs : resolve provider profile
ProviderManager --> Secrets : resolve credentials_ref
ProviderManager --> ProviderAdapter : initialize + validate

Orchestrator --> ProviderAdapter : recognize_once / start_stream / push_audio
ProviderAdapter --> Backend : provider-specific call
Backend --> SpeechEngine : local inference or cloud SDK/API

Orchestrator --> RosGraph : publish final/partial/status
RosGraph --> GatewayROS : observer subscriptions
GatewayROS --> GatewayAPI : runtime snapshot

note right of Orchestrator
  Two runtime modes:
  1. segmented: AudioSegment from VAD
  2. provider_stream: preprocessed chunks directly to provider
end note

note bottom of GatewayAPI
  GUI does not talk to runtime nodes directly.
  All browser traffic crosses the gateway boundary first.
end note

@enduml
